# pyo3 & maturin

## env in conda

```shell
# https://pyo3.rs/v0.17.3/ this is conda
conda env create
# done
conda activate test_pyo3
pip install maturin

```

## develop

```shell
maturin develop
```

test:

```shell
python

>>> import test_pyo3
>>> test_pyo3.sum_as_string(5, 20)
'25'
>>> exit()

```

## build and publish

```shell
#maturin build
maturin build -f -r

```

```shell
maturin publish
```

